note(`"Kolmogorov-Smirnov Distance(corrected p-value):"' `" 1. (Hetero=Aggregated) `d1'(`p1') 2. (Hetero=Not aggregated) `d2'(`p2')"' `"Only included both CCEIs>=0.90"' ///
